sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as 用户
    participant M as Manager
    participant E as Editor
    participant V as Verifier
    participant S as Sandbox

    U->>M: "做一个 Todo App"
    M->>M: 拆解 todo[]
    M->>E: 创建 src/App.tsx
    E->>S: create_file
    E->>S: install_package react
    E->>V: 准备好了
    V->>S: npm run build
    S-->>V: error: missing import
    V->>M: fail (附 error)
    M->>E: 修 import
    E->>S: str_replace_editor
    E->>V: 重试
    V->>S: build + preview
    S-->>V: ok
    V->>M: pass
    M->>U: 完成 + preview link
